title: Hidden Setting: Tiddler Scroll-Offset
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

This setting defines the minimum distance in pixel a scroll-target must have to trigger a scroll event
The default is 50

It can be configured in a tiddler titled:
$:/config/Tiddlerscrolloffset
